# nornir_http

Collection of simple plugins for [nornir](github.com/nornir-automation/nornir/)


## Install

```bash
pip install nornir_http
```

## Tasks

- `http_method` - Simple task for sending http requests.


## Examples

Examples can be found in the file [`demo.py`](demo.py)
